Package: saneshell
Version: 0.1.0
Section: shells
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Recommends: saneshell-intel
Maintainer: Scout <scout@localhost>
Description: Next-generation shell with proactive completions, inline previews,
 and post-hoc error detection. Go core with optional Java/GraalVM intelligence daemon.
 .
 Features: vi-mode line editor, PTY passthrough for interactive commands,
 native cd/pushd/popd, IPC over Unix socket, tab completion from PATH+filesystem.
